{"tid":1393095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作為僱主／員工，8月5號我都有D野想同大家講","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T03:32:12.000Z","uid":30000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b787c0a408a775d0bea1d60f38d3315f0add7fed","tid":1393095,"uid":30000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"相信大家呢2個月大家都攰，但係我地個特首林鄭到而家都未肯正面回應我地香港人的訴求，出動左幾多次的防暴黑警及速龍去鎮壓我地個和平示威行動，甚至於仲同鄉黑勾結添，數次既記者會特首都係講對示威者行動予以譴責及繼續支持警隊執法！我屌佢老母警隊執法就唔洗好似爛仔咁企左係我同我朋友架車面前咁曬馬啦屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為僱主／中高層的你同我，好應該明白如果今次的行動完左之後，有可能有堆為你衝的年青人而面臨入獄的危機，有機會自己最黃金的時間可能係官司及獄中度過<br />\n若果真係罪成，出黎之後我同我Partner願意優先請呢班人，如果需要我地support，我本人會係盡可能係做你地的避風港先，令前線無後顧之憂<br />\n<br />\n我地暫時唔方便開名講自己做邊行同做咩生意，因為我地仲覺得香港仲有希望。另外我同我Partner 係8月5號當日都唔會返工支持今次行動同出去集會，同時都同左我地同事講如果8月5號真係發夢而身體不適，我地絕不會好似中共咁玩清算，就算唔洗假紙我都會照出糧<br />\n<br />\n明白唔係